Software engineering

1. Decouple
To be cohesion 

2. Should be rewarded: Spot and fix a bug in a very early stage/write elegent code

3. TDD: Test driven development   
(1)Write unit tests, make sure all fail initially (other wise irrelevant factors influence the function/tests)  
(2)Finish functionalities  
(3)Try to pass all the tests  
(4)Refine/Refactor, Try to pass all again  
Exp: If no enough unit tests for some infrastructure code, difficult to refine it. coz you don't know whether that will cause some issues (bugs) or not.

